# Integrate Google OAuth callback

Wire the OAuth callback handler into the authentication middleware and session management.

## Prerequisites

- [ ] @step add-oauth-endpoints
- [ ] Google OAuth credentials are provisioned in the staging
    environment
- [ ] @step add-oauth-identities-table

## Tasks

- [ ] 1. Implement `/auth/google/callback` handler

- [ ] 2. Exchange authorization code for tokens

- [ ] 3. @spec auth/google OAuth callback: Valid callback

- [ ] 4. @spec auth/google OAuth callback: User denies authorization
